Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.96,0:02:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.96,0:02:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位旅客请注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.53,0:02:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本班机即将进入Satyros圆轴轨道的减速力场内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.47,0:02:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后将由下行电磁平台降下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.50,0:02:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并预定于25分钟之后在13点11分到达可汗宇宙港
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.31,0:02:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.01,0:02:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达这里的话就不会有问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.11,0:02:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.81,0:02:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.22,0:03:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,批准草案被抢走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.52,0:03:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…还是在我们没察觉的状况下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.59,0:03:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.96,0:03:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必这次也跟太空船上的旅客无关吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.06,0:03:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讲这种话嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.03,0:03:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，手段看来似乎是一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.03,0:03:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手段啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要用什么方法才能不留痕迹地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.27,0:03:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从轨道电梯的太空船中把东西给偷走呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.47,0:03:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算起来是第18次了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.71,0:03:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第19次啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.35,0:03:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快点点抓到嫌犯才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.75,0:03:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第六话 双璧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.09,0:03:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点恕难照办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.22,0:03:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.56,0:03:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们Satyros是个贸易行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.19,0:03:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且，更以身为银河大动脉的重要地位为傲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.80,0:03:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.03,0:03:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是这个Caune港一分钟内就有多少舰艇起降？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.20,0:03:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然想要让他们停止通行…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.37,0:03:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不让他们通行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.47,0:03:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是检查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.31,0:04:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是进行临检
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.51,0:04:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是针对犯罪所…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.34,0:04:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影响都是一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.11,0:04:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是GOTT的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.22,0:04:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方也不能做出比现在更多的管制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.42,0:04:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?等等…可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.22,0:04:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就够了，我们就是为此才会被派遣到这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.39,0:04:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藉由利用这个宇宙港的国家、企业与舰船的协助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.56,0:04:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以获得许多详细的资料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.57,0:04:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后将资料完整拷贝并传将送到Aineias
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.77,0:04:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能在GOTT总局内进行资料分析
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.17,0:04:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.84,0:04:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOTT的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.64,0:04:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ES成员！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.55,0:04:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是GOTT的Dextera
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.98,0:04:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是同样隶属GOTT的Sinistra
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.92,0:04:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这两位在的话就不用担心被抢或骇客入侵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.82,0:04:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以按照原定计划开始进行了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.30,0:04:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们的协助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.93,0:05:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.10,0:05:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是UAS0003
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.11,0:05:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五分钟后，引擎加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.01,0:05:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用通往Aineias的205航道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.05,0:05:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UAS0003收到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请开始加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.92,0:05:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,STC准许离陆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.95,0:05:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这上面有ES成员?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.12,0:05:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个传说中的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.79,0:05:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，不过这是个陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.96,0:05:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是真的冒冒失失的冲上去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.83,0:05:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被一网打尽是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.10,0:05:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.14,0:05:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这玩意在满了交易船的机密资料对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.71,0:05:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么眼睁睁看着他飞走未免令人大不甘心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.81,0:05:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈，难道你想偷袭ES成员吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.65,0:05:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是要机密资料呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.05,0:05:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是躲开ES成员啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.25,0:05:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，这是个难题呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.26,0:05:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢…哈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.20,0:06:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，要登机了唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.50,0:06:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Montague小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.47,0:06:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Montague小姐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.64,0:06:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair·Montague
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.41,0:06:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.64,0:06:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.51,0:06:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Padoshika小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.65,0:06:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没问题吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.85,0:06:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没问题吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.08,0:06:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的任务很重大的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.35,0:06:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ES成员的Dextera\N跟Sinistra只是担任诱饵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.09,0:06:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而实际上负责运送的却是我们耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.39,0:06:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…我想我很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.70,0:06:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉，你真是靠不住啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.70,0:06:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然直到目前为止你只负责过柜台的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.90,0:06:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你也是GOTT的职员吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.34,0:06:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请用心一点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.84,0:06:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…Padoshika小姐倒是你没问题吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.88,0:06:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.32,0:06:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.29,0:06:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有担任S0成员七年的资历了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不、不过呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.29,0:07:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Montague小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.79,0:07:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是“太太”喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.20,0:07:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，这是你的先生是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.97,0:07:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看起来好温柔喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.60,0:07:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他目前担任C军团第三分遣队的队长喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.54,0:07:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gurikku要保佑我哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，蒙大奇小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.25,0:07:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是别多说了快办理登机手续吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.21,0:07:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的，Padoshika太…Padoshika小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.29,0:07:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为虽然是『太太』但你真的大年轻了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.66,0:07:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.66,0:07:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么称呼根本就不重要啦快点办理登机手续吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.56,0:07:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明自己都先说不是『小姐』了还好意思说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.00,0:07:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行李让我帮您托运吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.00,0:07:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不用了 这是我的随身行李
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.57,0:07:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.61,0:07:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦请填写申请表并让我确认携带物品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.75,0:07:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.08,0:08:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.15,0:08:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为最近出了很多怪事所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.82,0:08:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦请填写一下这张表格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.05,0:08:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.39,0:08:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，我在赶时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.02,0:08:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BNL的3522航班要去哪里坐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.96,0:08:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3522的话，马上就要出发了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.80,0:08:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请走A82通道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.57,0:08:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.31,0:08:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱、箱子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.68,0:08:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Padoshika小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.35,0:08:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Montague小姐，我…\N我怎么会让这种事情发生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.09,0:08:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是老把戏了 但是效果倒还是挺不错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.30,0:08:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个故意引起你的注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.36,0:08:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个就趁机下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.27,0:08:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢，蒙大奇小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.34,0:09:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以叫我Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.94,0:09:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比较习惯人家这么叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.41,0:09:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.48,0:09:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.12,0:09:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请填写随身行李的申请书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.95,0:09:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，对喔，对呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.19,0:09:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，还有这个也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.69,0:09:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，您是要托运物品是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.99,0:09:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.66,0:09:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上给您寄物证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.27,0:09:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是B0L3600
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.40,0:09:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五分钟後，引擎加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.34,0:09:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用通往Aineias的224航道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.05,0:09:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位小姐，您的行李…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.95,0:09:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起！我先生说行李绝对不可以离手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.96,0:09:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终於要出发了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.33,0:09:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没去护卫没关系吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.73,0:09:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在担心Eclair吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.53,0:09:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的话，就请现在去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.63,0:10:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有我的工作要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.50,0:10:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到真的分开行动了耶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.63,0:10:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还蛮无惰的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.44,0:10:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不喜欢老是黏在一起的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.81,0:10:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为分开时会很难过吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.44,0:10:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…被我说中了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.55,0:10:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本航班目前正航行于圆轴轨道中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.65,0:10:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过23分的圆环加速後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.29,0:10:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将前往空间跳跃之门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.06,0:11:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前加速正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将超过百分之五十
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.93,0:11:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外，还请各位旅客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.24,0:11:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万不可以解开您的安全带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.21,0:11:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.64,0:11:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，乖乖的别说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.91,0:11:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来到目前为止还蛮顺利的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.68,0:11:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…害我满头汗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.65,0:11:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你好紧张哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.85,0:11:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，好羡慕你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.49,0:11:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神态轻松自如，是因为年轻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.29,0:11:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有，Padoshika小姐还不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.63,0:11:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.59,0:11:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.10,0:11:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次接到这么重要的任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.20,0:11:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕…也是最后一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.30,0:11:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一次?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.21,0:11:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.67,0:11:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和Gurikku…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.28,0:11:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是我丈夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.81,0:11:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他商量过后才下决定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.38,0:11:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把这趟任务当做最后的工作\N之后就要向GOTT请辞了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.12,0:11:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样，为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.39,0:12:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.36,0:12:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定要让这趟任务顺利成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.76,0:12:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.30,0:12:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高周波?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.80,0:12:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…还有催眠瓦斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.00,0:12:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是强盗吗?居然用这种手段…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.45,0:13:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被算计了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.82,0:13:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的行动根本早就被犯人们看透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.56,0:13:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快退开…Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.26,0:13:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就是轨道电梯上的强盗对吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.84,0:13:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.77,0:13:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有我在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.44,0:13:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是他还是这个箱子你们碰都别想碰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.78,0:13:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.39,0:13:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.62,0:13:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳米离子防护罩，展开！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.69,0:13:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你们再靠近的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.85,0:14:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.25,0:14:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你们快点乖乖投降吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.49,0:14:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了，已经没事了Padoshika小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.16,0:14:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那犯人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.53,0:14:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能对防护罩没辙，所以就走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.47,0:14:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.63,0:14:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到居然会找上我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.50,0:14:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，从他们能在空调中混入瓦斯这点来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.41,0:14:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员不可能不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.78,0:14:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，驾驶员也是共犯吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.71,0:14:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.82,0:14:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.88,0:14:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是用纳米微粒的技术把瓦斯中和掉的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.99,0:14:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.32,0:14:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.76,0:14:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们直接去逮捕他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.93,0:14:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.23,0:14:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来…来了，Padoshika小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.87,0:14:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.74,0:15:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不错嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.24,0:15:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我是第一次使用这种装备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.11,0:15:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到真的还挺有效的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.35,0:15:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.38,0:15:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Padoshika小姐，是操纵杆快把操纵杆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.89,0:15:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急求救、紧急求救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.13,0:15:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是B0L3600
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.30,0:15:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正被卷入连续强盗案件中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.57,0:15:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状况还在持续中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.97,0:15:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外，连正规驾驶员也是共犯之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此已遭到逮捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.57,0:15:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是自动驾驶系统跟身为乘客的我在操纵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.31,0:15:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急求救、紧急求救有人可以回应吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.58,0:15:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair那边要是绑好的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.55,0:15:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair，跑哪里去了呀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.05,0:15:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这种时候了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.53,0:16:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵～锵～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.31,0:16:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种武装…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.54,0:16:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是轨道警察监守自盗吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.28,0:16:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是无药可救啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.65,0:16:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair，你在那里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Padoshika小姐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.69,0:16:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万不要离开现在的位置哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.73,0:16:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个女人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.14,0:16:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Padoshika小姐，漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.61,0:16:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧，还有增援?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.56,0:17:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?船不受控制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.23,0:17:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然我们的身分都暴露了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.06,0:17:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只能伪装成交通意外事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.16,0:17:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个适当的地方击落它吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.03,0:17:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.07,0:17:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.94,0:17:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺负两个弱女子居然还得送来三只恶狼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.21,0:17:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该上场啰 可以起床了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.08,0:17:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以到那边去啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.99,0:17:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.63,0:17:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们上啰，Donnersclac
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.57,0:17:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.39,0:18:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二回合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.00,0:18:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个臭丫头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.57,0:18:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好，逮到你了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.74,0:18:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.01,0:18:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Donnersclac
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.52,0:18:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不、不会吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.39,0:18:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼…就差最后一击了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.63,0:18:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.83,0:18:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.94,0:19:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.91,0:19:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.81,0:19:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不习惯让女士等待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.41,0:19:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…我们是不是来迟了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.25,0:19:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会，来得刚刚好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.35,0:19:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.15,0:19:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在对方的大本营\N应该也已经被压制住了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.27,0:19:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果，犯罪集团主要来自\N轨道警察的部分人员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.27,0:19:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了袭击你们的手段之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.57,0:19:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用电脑制造虚拟体验、调包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.08,0:19:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窜改加速、减速的行程表等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.91,0:19:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎各种手段都用上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.45,0:19:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还有被害者本人其实就是委托人的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.32,0:19:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用来诈领保险金或是假造帐簿等等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.96,0:19:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然动机各有不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.73,0:19:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他们的行为都是犯罪这一点是不会变的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.09,0:19:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢两位
